veServers\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/weloveservers1-300x225.jpg.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a><a href=\"http://www.weloveservers.net\">WeLoveServers</a> also loves the LowEndBox community! Chris sent in these two great Black Friday specials which are available in five locations!</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>LEB 1GB</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>1.2GB vSwap</li><li>4 vCPU Cores</li><li>30GB Disk space</li><li>1TB Bandwidth</li><li>100Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>$19/Year | <a href=\"https://core.weloveservers.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=64\" target=\"_blank\">Order</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>LEB 3GB</strong><p></p><ul><li>3GB RAM</li><li>4GB vSwap</li><li>4 vCPU Core</li><li>80GB Disk space</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>100Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>$7/Month | <a href=\"https://core.weloveservers.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=88\" target=\"_blank\">Order</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>WeLoveServers have been featured on LowEndBox a <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/weloveservers-net/\">quote some times before</a>, since we first listed them in January 2013. As an extra bonus exclusively for LEB, anyone who orders can claim a free upgrade from a 100Mbps port to 1Gbps! After completing the order, open a ticket and they will have the upgrade to 1Gbps completed within ~30 minutes. They utilise Intel Xeon E31240 processors with hardware RAID10. Reviews have been consistently very good. As always, you are welcome to share your experience with them in the comments.</p><p><span id=\"more-4677\"></span>WeLoveServers accept payments via Paypal. Refunds are offered on a case by case basis. TUN/TAP and PPTP modules are supported. Additional IPv4 Addresses are $1.60 each. WeLoveServers offers complimentary DNS hosting management to all VPS customers. Servers will be setup instantly. VPN Servers, adult content and IRC are allowed. Anything illegal in the United States and P2P/Torrents are prohibited. For more information, take a look at their&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.weloveservers.net/tos-acceptable-use-policy/\" target=\"_blank\">Terms of Service</a>.</p><p><strong>Network test</strong></p><p>Los Angeles, CA, USA: 192.210.195.2<br>\nDallas, TX, USA: 192.227.137.2<br>\nBuffalo, NY, USA: 192.227.135.130<br>\nOrlando, FL, USA: 72.29.70.131<br>\nKent UK: 109.73.162.6</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fblack-friday-weloveservers-19year-1gb-and-7month-3gb-openvz-vps-in-five-locations%2F&amp;t=%5BBLACK%20FRIDAY%5D%20WeLoveServers%20-%20%2419%2Fyear%201GB%20and%20%247%2Fmonth%203GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20five%20locations\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=%5BBLACK%20FRIDAY%5D%20WeLoveServers%20-%20%2419%2Fyear%201GB%20and%20%247%2Fmonth%203GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20five%20locations&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fblack-friday-weloveservers-19year-1gb-and-7month-3gb-openvz-vps-in-five-locations%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\"